    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>《Doomed Hell 64》是一款复古风格的FPS游戏，你将在充满怪物与混乱的地狱关卡中奋战。迎战无尽的敌人，揭开地狱的隐藏秘密，歼灭一切生命！</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3297340/extras/43b47f32c7e96e1248212fc9d1d198b3.avif?t=1772361117\" width=616 height=99 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3297340/extras/26f030db9c0b6795db8c9929090d09a9.poster.avif?t=1772361117\" width=600 height=330 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3297340/extras/26f030db9c0b6795db8c9929090d09a9.webm?t=1772361117\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3297340/extras/26f030db9c0b6795db8c9929090d09a9.mp4?t=1772361117\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >关于 Doomed Hell 64</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《Doomed Hell 64》是一款复古第一人称地牢探险游戏，将你带入充满混乱和怪物的地狱深渊。在战役模式中冲破激烈关卡，对抗无尽敌潮，并在街机模式和死亡竞速等多种玩法中测试你的技巧。通过程序生成的关卡、快节奏的战斗以及大量强力武器，每一场战斗都独一无二，充满肾上腺素！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3297340/extras/cf01a3a6df479b3ada109035cc0cdff1.avif?t=1772361117\" width=616 height=99 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3297340/extras/dec52712c97bcefe1801a19d7438acea.poster.avif?t=1772361117\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3297340/extras/dec52712c97bcefe1801a19d7438acea.webm?t=1772361117\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3297340/extras/dec52712c97bcefe1801a19d7438acea.mp4?t=1772361117\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >主要特色</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在关卡中探索隐藏的秘密，解锁15种以上独特升级，丰富游戏体验。用25种以上的武器皮肤自定义你的武器，并迎战可怕的Boss。不论是寻找彩蛋还是在生存模式中奋战，《Doomed Hell 64》都将带来无尽的动作体验和极高的可玩性！</p>",
